The ceasefire will speed up the pace of negotiations with Russia, — Orban

More based on the results of the negotiations:

🔹Hungary is ready to support the modernization of the Ukrainian economy;
🔹Ukraine and Hungary are preparing an agreement on bilateral relations;
🔹Hungary intends to help Ukraine during its presidency of the Council of the EU.

⚡️🇩🇪🇺🇦 Germany has updated the list of military aid delivered to the Armed Forces of Ukraine:

🟠 8 Leopard 1A5 MBTs;
🟠 10 Sonobot 5 USVs;
🟠 2 Bergepanzer 2 ARVs;
🟠 10 ground surveillance radars Ground Observer 12;
🟠 21,000 35mm APDS-T rounds for Gepard/Cheetah SPAAGs;
🟠 24,810 combat helmets M92;
🟠 1 Forward Surgical Team system / role 1 (already known).

